class="block-intro-text"><p>The state of Alabama welcomes new businesses with a great business climate, strong training programs for the workforce, a low tax burden, and good economic incentives for startup businesses. It is a fast-growing region, with a network of highways, over 90 airports, and a large harbor.</p></div></div></div></div><div
