1 Month</div></div><div
class="how-to-desc"><div
class="how-to-image">
<picture>
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-how-to-start-a-business-in-alabama-complete-800x800-20200914.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=250&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="250" height="250" alt="How to Start a Business in Alabama:">
</picture></div><p>Alabama offers four main ways to form a business. Aside from sole proprietorships, all business structures must be registered with the state. Every business in Alabama must register with the Alabama Department of Revenue and obtain a privilege license to operate in the state. Depending on your profession, you may also need an occupation license.</p></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-business-in-alabama-section1" class="how-to-section"><div
class="section-title">
<span>1.&nbsp;</span><h3 id=form-your-business>Form your business.</h3></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-business-in-alabama-section1-step1" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>1.1&nbsp;</span><h4 id=review-alabama-formation-options>Review Alabama formation options.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-review-alabama-formation-options-288x288-20200914.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Review Alabama formation options."></div></div><p>Alabama offers <a
href="#alabama-business-types">four basic ways of forming your business</a>, which we cover in detail below. Review these closely and pick the one that fits your business best.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-business-in-alabama-section1-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>1.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=name-your-business>Name your business.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-name-your-business-288x288-2020091.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Name your business."></div></div><p>Before you can reserve a business name, you need to verify that your name is available and not currently being used by another business. All business entities in Alabama are required to reserve their business name before registering their business with the state.</p><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Visit the Alabama Secretary of State website and perform a <a
href="https://www.sos.alabama.gov/government-records/business-entity-records">business entity search</a> to find out if your name is available.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p><strong>To register by mail</strong>, download the <a
href="https://www.sos.alabama.gov/sites/default/files/2022-09/domesticEntityNameReservation.pdf">Name Reservation Request Form</a>.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Read the instructions carefully and take note of the name requirements for each business structure.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Complete the form on your computer as the information on the application must be typed and not handwritten.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Print the completed form and sign it.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Mail the completed form along with the $25.00 processing fee to the address indicated in the instructions on the form.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p><strong>To register online</strong>, visit the Alabama SOS <a
href="https://www.alabamainteractive.org/sos/welcome.action">online services</a>.</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
<path
d="M12 0c-6.627 0-12 5.373-12 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12-5.373-12-12-12zm7 14h-5v5h-4v-5h-5v-4h5v-5h4v5h5v4z" fill="#4949E7"/>
</svg>
</span><p>Unless you are an Alabama Interactive subscriber, select "Non-Subscriber."</p></div><div
class="step-direction">
<span
class="icon">
<svg
xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
