</svg>
</span><p>Submit the report.</p></div></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-business-in-alabama-section3-step2" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>3.2&nbsp;</span><h4 id=obtain-mandatory-insurance>Obtain mandatory insurance.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-obtain-mandatory-insurance-288x288-20200917.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Obtain mandatory insurance."></div></div><p>In Alabama, businesses with more than five employees are required by law to carry Workers' Compensation Insurance.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-business-in-alabama-section3-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
